Umurenge wa Muganza uhererereye mu majyepfo yuburengerazuba bw' akarere ka Rusizi (-2.6133136549023903, 29.01959164694231)<ref>https://www.google.com/maps/search/muganza+sector,+cimerwa/@-2.616829,28.9766763,13z</ref>.Ugizwe n'utugali dutatu aritwo Shara, Gakoni na Cyarukara  <ref>{{Cite web |title=Archive copy |url=https://rusizi.gov.rw/index.php?id=156 |accessdate=2021-03-08 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118173804/https://rusizi.gov.rw/index.php?id=156 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>. Akagali ka Shara gaherereye kuva ku ryambere ( First street) kugera ku ryagatatu (Third street), aka Gakoni gaherereye Kuryakane kugera kuryagatandatu, naho aka Cyarukara kava kuryakarindwi kugera kurya munani. Imwe mu mirenge bihana imbibi Bugarama, Rwimbogo, Gitambi na Gikundamvura. Uyu murenge niwo uherereyemo uruganda rwa CIMERWA ltd rukora isima<ref>https://cimerwa.rw/#</ref>, ukaba unazwiho guhinga umuceri dore ko ufite ubuso bunini buhigwamo umuceli mu kibaya cyimbo. Bikaba byumvikana ko abaturage baho batuzwe cyane n'ubuhinzi.
